Title: Dominoes Falling
Plot: When a gang execution hits close to home for Claudette, Vic, Tavon, and Dutch work together to find the culprit before anyone else gets hurt.  Shane, Lemonhead, and Ronnie are forced to choose between hitting the money train without Vic or letting it go.  Meanwhile, Danny receives some life changing news and Julien's harassment reaches a whole new level.
GuestStars: David Rees Snell, Cathy Cahlin Ryan, Brian J. White, Ron Canada, Camillia Sanes, Monnae Michaell, Frank Grillo, Tracie Thoms
